                    <statement>
                        <p>Here is a graph of the foreign-born US population (in millions) during Census years 1960 to 2010. (Source: <url href="http://www.pewhispanic.org/2015/09/28/chapter-5-u-s-foreign-born-population-trends/" />.)</p>
